{"tid":1362492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Sydney人同我入哂嚟","createTime":"2019-07-25T01:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T03:15:02.000Z","uid":22342,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"786c09eab8b5891a708f6adbc61497116e6ba33a","tid":1362492,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:35:16.000Z","msg":"New South Wales大家，香港需要你<br />\n近日香港發生元朗白衣人持鐵通亂打人事件，另外在上環干一帶警方在沒有舉起黑旗警告情况下，密集式發射催淚彈、胡椒彈及以水平線直射36發橡膠子彈。<br />\n以及鑑於7月24號昆士蘭大學 university of Queensland 一事，我們身於澳洲本該享有言論自由，可以合法地表達自己意見。但中國人用不法手段打壓，對此我們表示憤怒。希望大家可以踴躍出席。<br />\n香港需要大家既聲音<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/468679683965501/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F468679683965501%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=53851a50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/468679683965501/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今個星期日同我出曬嚟</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"13d738e65742a666963f225f2f076f28949dd637","tid":1362492,"uid":176148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:39:57.000Z","msg":"又r frd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1562024aa5e1d0596785dc639d0e78f8a4ec2c","tid":1362492,"uid":258243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"UQ人 推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fe3b98a4792bb5b30c533a08716992338554da","tid":1362492,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:45:27.000Z","msg":"Queensland巴打俾人恰唔係唔出黎啊嘛！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed6edbe0ca7e3f34486ed4c7f97f6e837349caf","tid":1362492,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src